About Heiler Communities
Your ideal retirement awaits in our affordable, active communities, where comfort, convenience, and a vibrant social atmosphere create the perfect place to enjoy life.
A Legacy of Quality Living Since 1946
The Heiler family has been a trusted name in manufactured housing since 1946. Now in its fourth generation, Heiler Communities offers affordable, high-quality homes in Central Florida and Lower Alabama. With a focus on customer satisfaction, we provide a variety of living options to suit every lifestyle. Our experienced team, including Suncrest Homes, is here to guide you through every step, from home selection to move-in.
Locations
Find Your Perfect Home
At Heiler Communities, we operate seven vibrant and welcoming communities, each offering its unique charm. With six of our communities located in sunny Florida and one in the picturesque coastal area of Lower Alabama, you’ll find the perfect location to match your lifestyle and needs.
Central Florida
With five communities in Pasco County and Lake Hammock Village in Central Florida, Heiler Communities offers affordable living near beaches, golf courses, and attractions like Disney. Whether you prefer the “Gateway to Tropical Florida” or peaceful lakeside living, you’ll find welcoming neighborhoods and a variety of housing options to suit your lifestyle.
Lower Alabama
Our community in this scenic coastal area is just minutes from the Florida state line, offering the best of both worlds with close proximity to the beach and all the amenities you need for comfortable living.
View Communities
Affordable Living With A Personal Touch
At Heiler Communities, we believe in providing more than just a place to live. We create communities where residents can enjoy a worry-free lifestyle, surrounded by friendly faces and excellent amenities. Here are a few reasons why so many people choose to call Heiler Communities home:
Affordable Options
Our communities offer homes at various price points, so you can find something that fits your budget without sacrificing comfort or convenience.
Prime Locations
Whether you’re drawn to the sunny shores of Florida or the peaceful coastal areas of Alabama, our communities are situated in prime locations.
Experienced Team
With decades of experience, our team, alongside Suncrest Homes, is ready to guide you through every step of the home buying process.
Active, Friendly Communities
Enjoy amenities like clubhouses, pools, and planned activities that create a welcoming environment and foster a true sense of community.
Our Available Homes
We provide a wide selection of new and used manufactured homes to suit any budget. Plus, we offer flexible financing options to make owning your Florida or Alabama dream home easier than ever.
